00:15.052 --> 00:16.586
Step aside, Major.

00:16.621 --> 00:18.789
We'd all understand if
you pulled that trigger.

00:20.458 --> 00:24.028
But the lives of thousands
of people are at stake.

00:42.519 --> 00:44.020
Hmm...

00:44.055 --> 00:45.489
Secure him.

00:48.393 --> 00:50.061
Dress his wounds.

01:02.410 --> 01:04.111
<i>John Porter...</i>

01:14.322 --> 01:15.556
<i>Blood.</i>

01:20.695 --> 01:21.895
Sit forward.

01:25.767 --> 01:27.934
Enjoy your stay
at the organ farm?

01:27.969 --> 01:30.104
Actually, I thought
the food was shit.

01:30.138 --> 01:31.806
So I discharged myself.

01:34.277 --> 01:36.278
We're secure!

01:36.312 --> 01:38.848
Careful.

01:41.552 --> 01:43.153
He's clean.

01:46.691 --> 01:49.660
Sergeant Richmond...

01:49.694 --> 01:54.865
All your training to do
this...woman's work.

02:05.211 --> 02:08.113
Sergeant. We have
a hit! Target 2.

02:08.148 --> 02:09.247
Purchasing train ticket.

02:09.282 --> 02:11.150
Where?

02:11.184 --> 02:12.384
Big screen.

02:14.154 --> 02:16.522
Kobanya Station,
south-east suburb.

02:16.556 --> 02:17.923
<i>Satellite lock on Kobanya.</i>

02:17.958 --> 02:19.391
Target's carrying a case.

02:19.426 --> 02:22.528
Right, he's on the train.
Where's it going?

02:22.562 --> 02:25.798
Arrives Nyugati Main
Station in 12 minutes.

02:25.832 --> 02:27.700
If there is a bomb
in that case...

02:27.734 --> 02:30.069
He'll need a trigger mechanism.
Something like a cell phone.

02:30.103 --> 02:32.538
Remember we're
dealing with VX.

02:32.572 --> 02:34.006
You will shoot
to kill.

02:34.040 --> 02:35.774
Copy that.
Yes, Ma'am.

02:39.445 --> 02:41.446
Is it just me?
What?

02:41.481 --> 02:43.415
Sinclair.

02:43.450 --> 02:45.128
You gotta wonder about
a guy that's gonna step

02:45.153 --> 02:46.553
between a bullet and Latif.

03:05.527 --> 03:09.527
